{"type":"message","id":"cbd3d7ea","parentId":"9df8fe6e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:01:01.966Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is complaining that after the gateway restarts, it can't start back up on its own - they have to manually restart it. Also, any tasks that were running before the restart can't continue.\n\nThis is a fundamental issue with how the gateway restart works. When the gateway stops, all the agent sessions also stop, so there's no agent to restart the gateway. The startup script only runs at login, not during operation.\n\nThe user is frustrated because:\n1. Gateway doesn't auto-start after a restart - requires manual restart\n2. Any tasks that were running before the restart are lost\n\nThis is a design limitation. Let me think about solutions:\n\n1. The startup script only runs at Windows login, not when the gateway stops unexpectedly\n2. There's no watchdog/monitor process that would restart the gateway if it stops\n3. When the gateway restarts, all sessions are lost\n\nPossible solutions:\n1. Create a watchdog service/script that monitors the gateway and restarts it if it stops\n2. Use Windows Task Scheduler to periodically check if the gateway is running and start it if not\n3. Create a more robust startup script that can be triggered by events\n\nLet me explain the issue to the user and propose solutions.","thinkingSignature":"4bdc0714ff6ff6d91b46d9b6b8fdf119f7d47197a6fd633fcef96a5164c19261"},{"type":"text","text":"čŋæŊå äļš Gateway åæ­Ēæķïžå―åį agent session äđäžæ­åžïžæäŧĨæ æģčŠåĻéåŊã\n\n**éŪéĒæ đæšïž**\n- Gateway åæ­Ē â å―å session æ­åž â æēĄæ agent æĨæ§čĄéåŊå―äŧĪ\n- åŊåĻčæŽåŠåĻ**įŧå― Windows æķ**čŋčĄïžäļæŊæįŧ­įæ§\n\n**č§ĢåģæđæĄïž**\n1. **ååŧš Windows įæ§äŧŧåĄ** - įĻčŪĄåäŧŧåĄåŪææĢæĨ Gateway įķæïžåĶæåäšå°ąčŠåĻåŊåĻ\n2. **ååŧšäļäļŠ watchdog čæŽ** - åå°æįŧ­įæ§ Gateway čŋįĻ\n\nčĶæåļŪä― ååŧšäļäļŠįæ§čæŽåïžčŋæ · Gateway æåĪåæ­ĒæķäžčŠåĻéåŊïžäļéčĶä― æåĻæä―ã"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64,"output":372,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":151714,"totalTokens":152150,"cost":{"input":0.000025600000000000002,"output":0.000558,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0227571,"total":0.0233407}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773918043105}}
