{"type":"message","id":"80a94009","parentId":"8d13888d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:02:02.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a watchdog script that monitors the Gateway and restarts it if it stops. Let me create this script.\n\nI'll create:\n1. A PowerShell script that monitors the Gateway process\n2. A Windows scheduled task to run the monitor\n\nLet me create this.","thinkingSignature":"ef81b271bf063dcc2267433ea86cd38053cf7dd73bc0081a8a035acbd93cc85f"},{"type":"text","text":"åĨ―įïžčŪĐæååŧšäļäļŠįæ§čæŽïž\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m4hihje2kovq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw Gateway Watchdog\n# čŠåĻįæ§ Gateway čŋįĻïžåĶæåæ­ĒåčŠåĻéåŊ\n\n$GatewayPort = 18789\n$CheckInterval = 30  # æŊ30į§æĢæĨäļæŽĄ\n$LogFile = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\gateway-watchdog.log\"\n\nfunction Write-Log {\n    param([string]$Message)\n    $Timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    $LogMessage = \"$Timestamp $Message\"\n    Add-Content -Path $LogFile -Value $LogMessage\n    Write-Host $LogMessage\n}\n\nWrite-Log \"=== Gateway Watchdog Started ===\"\n\nwhile ($true) {\n    try {\n        # æĢæĨ Gateway æŊåĶåĻįåŽįŦŊåĢ\n        $Response = Invoke-WebRequest -Uri \"http://127.0.0.1:$GatewayPort\" -TimeoutSec 3 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        \n        if ($Response.StatusCode -eq 200) {\n            Write-Log \"Gateway is running (port $GatewayPort)\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Gateway not responding, trying to start...\"\n            Start-Process -FilePath \"openclaw\" -ArgumentList \"gateway\",\"start\" -NoNewWindow -WindowStyle Hidden\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds 5\n        }\n    } catch {\n        # įŦŊåĢæ ååšïžå°čŊåŊåĻ Gateway\n        Write-Log \"Gateway not responding, trying to start...\"\n        Start-Process -FilePath \"openclaw\" -ArgumentList \"gateway\",\"start\" -NoNewWindow -WindowStyle Hidden\n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 5\n    }\n    \n    Start-Sleep -Seconds $CheckInterval\n}\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\scripts\\gateway-watchdog.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64,"output":464,"cacheRead":151691,"cacheWrite":203,"totalTokens":152422,"cost":{"input":0.000025600000000000002,"output":0.000696,"cacheRead":0.00606764,"cacheWrite":0.000030449999999999998,"total":0.00681969}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773918110755}}
