{"type":"message","id":"e8cda737","parentId":"55b33c3e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:02:09.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to create a Windows scheduled task that runs this script. Let me create the task.","thinkingSignature":"331e754e6a8ceabb2cf12fa6c7c8e19549b34ea5414e13c0f5206ddef55cbd85"},{"type":"text","text":"į°åĻååŧš Windows čŪĄåäŧŧåĄæĨčŋčĄčŋäļŠįæ§čæŽïž\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f0fvdttfoctp_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"powershell -Command \"$action = New-ScheduledTaskAction -Execute 'powershell.exe' -Argument '-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -WindowStyle Hidden -File C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\scripts\\gateway-watchdog.ps1'; $trigger = New-ScheduledTaskTrigger -AtLogOn; $settings = New-ScheduledTaskSettingsSet -AllowStartIfOnBatteries -DontStopIfGoingOnBatteries -StartWhenAvailable; Register-ScheduledTask -TaskName 'OpenClaw Gateway Watchdog' -Action $action -Trigger $trigger -Settings $settings -Force\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":113969,"output":187,"cacheRead":38492,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":152648,"cost":{"input":0.045587600000000006,"output":0.0002805,"cacheRead":0.00153968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04740778000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773918122225}}
