{"type":"message","id":"e7208e08","parentId":"e120d08a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:18.969Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that sometimes when the gateway stops, it doesn't close completely, which causes the watchdog script to fail to start a new instance because the port is still in use. This is a common issue - when a process is killed but the port is still in TIME_WAIT state.\n\nI need to modify the watchdog script to:\n1. First kill any existing gateway processes that might be stuck\n2. Wait for the port to be released\n3. Then start the gateway fresh\n\nLet me update the watchdog script to handle this case.","thinkingSignature":"0a959ae93dd580a8bb540cd0cf915e0e8a707aa2fea1725abb150869f9382ce9"},{"type":"text","text":"æį―äšïžéŪéĒæŊ Gateway ææķåæēĄæåŪåĻåģé­ïžįŦŊåĢčŋčĒŦå įĻïžæäŧĨæ°åŪäūåŊåĻåĪąčīĨãčŪĐæäŋŪæđįæ§čæŽïžååžšåķåģé­æ§į Gateway čŋįĻååŊåĻïž\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2revl3yhu15i_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw Gateway Watchdog\n# čŠåĻįæ§ Gateway čŋįĻïžåĶæåæ­ĒåčŠåĻéåŊ\n\n$GatewayPort = 18789\n$CheckInterval = 30\n$LogDir = \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\logs\"\n$LogFile = \"$LogDir\\gateway-watchdog.log\"\n\n# Create log directory if not exists\nif (-not (Test-Path $LogDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $LogDir -Force | Out-Null\n}\n\nfunction Write-Log {\n    param([string]$Message)\n    $Timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    $LogMessage = \"$Timestamp $Message\"\n    Add-Content -Path $LogFile -Value $LogMessage -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n    Write-Host $LogMessage\n}\n\nfunction Test-GatewayRunning {\n    try {\n        $TCPClient = New-Object System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient\n        $TCPClient.Connect(\"127.0.0.1\", $GatewayPort)\n        $TCPClient.Close()\n        return $true\n    } catch {\n        return $false\n    }\n}\n\nfunction Stop-GatewayProcesses {\n    # åžšåķįŧæææåŊč―į gateway čŋįĻ\n    $GatewayProcesses = Get-Process -Name \"node\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Where-Object {\n        $_.CommandLine -like \"*openclaw*\" -or $_.CommandLine -like \"*gateway*\"\n    }\n    if ($GatewayProcesses) {\n        Write-Log \"Stopping existing gateway processes...\"\n        $GatewayProcesses | Stop-Process -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 3\n    }\n    \n    # įĄŪäŋįŦŊåĢéæū\n    $PortInUse = $true\n    for ($i = 0; $i -lt 10; $i++) {\n        try {\n            $TCPClient = New-Object System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient\n            $TCPClient.Connect(\"127.0.0.1\", $GatewayPort)\n            $TCPClient.Close()\n            Write-Log \"Port $GatewayPort still in use, waiting...\"\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n        } catch {\n            $PortInUse = $false\n            Write-Log \"Port $GatewayPort is free\"\n            break\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nWrite-Log \"=== Gateway Watchdog Started ===\"\n\nwhile ($true) {\n    if (Test-GatewayRunning) {\n        Write-Log \"Gateway is running (port $GatewayPort)\"\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"Gateway not responding, attempting restart...\"\n        \n        # åå°čŊæ­Ģåļļåģé­\n        try {\n            Stop-Process -Name \"node\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            Start-Sleep -Seconds 2\n        } catch {}\n        \n        # åžšåķæļį\n        Stop-GatewayProcesses\n        \n        # åŊåĻæ°åŪäū\n        Write-Log \"Starting gateway...\"\n        Start-Process -FilePath \"openclaw\" -ArgumentList \"gateway\",\"start\" -WindowStyle Hidden -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n        Start-Sleep -Seconds 5\n        \n        # éŠčŊåŊåĻæå\n        if (Test-GatewayRunning) {\n            Write-Log \"Gateway started successfully\"\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Gateway failed to start\"\n        }\n    }\n    \n    Start-Sleep -Seconds $CheckInterval\n}\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\scripts\\gateway-watchdog.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64,"output":894,"cacheRead":38492,"cacheWrite":97388,"totalTokens":136838,"cost":{"input":0.000025600000000000002,"output":0.001341,"cacheRead":0.00153968,"cacheWrite":0.0146082,"total":0.01751448}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773918294030}}
