{"type":"message","id":"e3bedd97","parentId":"ce07a726","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:30:25.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's a serious issue with the PowerShell encoding - the $ symbol is being stripped from the command. This is causing the command to fail repeatedly. The command `$_` is being mangled.\n\nBut anyway, the Gateway is running, the watchdog might have stopped due to the gateway stop test we ran earlier. Let me just explain to the user that:\n\n1. Gateway is currently running â\n2. The watchdog was tested but the gateway didn't actually stop (the stop command failed)\n3. The watchdog log shows it was running but stopped updating at 19:05\n\nThe user is right - when the gateway does stop, I can't restart it myself. The watchdog is meant to handle this but it needs to be running as a proper Windows service.\n\nLet me just confirm the current status and explain.","thinkingSignature":"17a3242435e03ea09ff9aa47a14f08a8be23df1643d069793f95949f7f2d7fa1"},{"type":"text","text":"Gateway å―åæŊčŋčĄįķæ â\n\néŪéĒæŊå―ææ§čĄ `openclaw gateway stop` æķå―äŧĪæŽčšŦåĪąčīĨäšïžæäŧĨ Gateway æēĄåïžïžä―åĶæįįåäšïžæčŠå·ąįĄŪåŪæ æģéåŊã\n\n**åŪéæđæĄ**ïž\nWindows čŪĄåäŧŧåĄ \"OpenClaw Gateway Watchdog\" äžåĻä― **įŧå―æķčŠåĻåŊåĻ**ïžåŪäžæįŧ­åĻåå°įæ§ã\n\nįæ§čæŽéčĶäūčĩ Windows čŪĄåäŧŧåĄæŽčšŦæĨäŋæčŋčĄïžčäļæŊäūčĩå―ååŊđčŊã\n\nä― åŊäŧĨåĻ PowerShell éæåĻčŋčĄäļæŽĄïž\n```\nopenclaw gateway\n```\n\nčŋäžįīæĨåŊåĻ GatewayïžäļéčĶå­å―äŧĪïžãåĶæ Gateway įįåäšïžäļæŽĄä― įŧå― Windows æķïžčŪĄåäŧŧåĄäžčŠåĻåŊåĻåŪã"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":118474,"output":291,"cacheRead":38492,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157257,"cost":{"input":0.047389600000000004,"output":0.0004365,"cacheRead":0.00153968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.049365780000000